headline: Jim Cramer on Axon: “They Just Keep Delivering Great Numbers”
summary: Axon Enterprise, Inc. (NASDAQ:AXON) is one of the stocks that Jim Cramer discussed. headline: DEA Marijuana Decision Showtime: MMJ Issues Demand Letter on DEA
summary: Duane Boise stated "In a September 3rd letter to DEA Terry Cole, that the Administrative Procedure Act requires agencies to act "within a reasonable time." If no decision is issued soon, MMJ will pursue all available remedies in federal appeals court ...
